1 Week Ago In a terse statement, Mba said, “CP Olugbenga Adeyanju, Adamawa State, CP Isaac Olutayo Akinmoyede, Imo State, CP Audu Adamu Madaki, FHQ, Abuja, and CP Edward Chuka Egbuka, Plateau State. “IGP Adamu calls on residents of the affected states to cooperate with the new commissioners in order to maintain law and order.” Inspector-General of Police (IG-P), Mohammed Adamu